WEBVTT

00:00:02.015 --> 00:00:04.979
zaynen di daytshn arayn in Kovne.

00:00:07.887 --> 00:00:09.958
beshas es iz geven

00:00:10.470 --> 00:00:11.629
der moment

00:00:12.444 --> 00:00:13.552
zaynen mir

00:00:13.750 --> 00:00:14.919
ge- arum

00:00:15.228 --> 00:00:16.606
fun di shtiber

00:00:17.456 --> 00:00:18.902
a sakh yidn

00:00:20.122 --> 00:00:22.816
arayn in a keler unter a moyer

00:00:23.413 --> 00:00:24.673
zikh bahaltn

00:00:25.286 --> 00:00:28.841
fun bombardirung. m'hot gehat moyre me zol nit bombardirn,

00:00:29.336 --> 00:00:30.815
me zol nit shisn.

00:00:33.234 --> 00:00:34.426
un

00:00:35.698 --> 00:00:36.874
mit a mol

00:00:37.098 --> 00:00:38.679
hern mir vi me klapt

00:00:38.870 --> 00:00:40.198
in tir fun

00:00:40.524 --> 00:00:41.362
keler.

00:00:42.296 --> 00:00:44.248
un me shrayt oyf daytsh:

00:00:44.692 --> 00:00:45.871
"AUFÖFFNEN!

00:00:45.871 --> 00:00:47.015
AUFÖFFNEN."

00:00:48.742 --> 00:00:53.023
ye, dort hobn mir shoyn farshtanen az di daytshn zaynen shoyn bay undz.

00:00:54.210 --> 00:00:56.196
men hot geefnt di tir

00:00:56.353 --> 00:00:57.394
fun keler,

00:00:58.580 --> 00:01:00.853
zaynen arayngelofn dray daytshn

00:01:02.023 --> 00:01:03.215
mit biksn

00:01:04.435 --> 00:01:06.894
arayngelofn. zey hobn gezen az s'iz do nor

00:01:07.541 --> 00:01:08.717
tsivile

00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:09.881
mentshn.

00:01:10.781 --> 00:01:13.121
nito keyn soldatn keyn rusishe.

00:01:16.569 --> 00:01:18.500
hobn zey gezogt,

00:01:18.645 --> 00:01:22.031
"ir kent zayn t- ru- ir kent zayt, zayn ruik.

00:01:23.353 --> 00:01:25.976
mit keyn tsivile kemfn mir nit."

00:01:26.778 --> 00:01:28.612
un zey zaynen aroys.

00:01:30.761 --> 00:01:32.122
zaynen aroys,

00:01:33.883 --> 00:01:35.314
un mir

00:01:35.317 --> 00:01:38.754
zaynen nokh geblibn in keler; mir hobn gehat moyre aroystsugeyn.

00:01:39.232 --> 00:01:42.669
ober shpeter, az s'iz shoyn gevorn tunkl fun ovnt,

00:01:43.738 --> 00:01:46.646
zaynen ale aroys in keler, un m'iz arayn tsurik

00:01:46.646 --> 00:01:48.355
bay zikh in di shtiber.

00:01:50.808 --> 00:01:53.064
m'iz arayn bay zikh in di shtiber.

00:01:54.437 --> 00:01:55.561
di nakht

00:01:55.601 --> 00:01:57.249
iz durkhgegangen

00:01:57.727 --> 00:01:59.038
gants ruik.

00:02:01.794 --> 00:02:03.560
ober in der fri

00:02:05.793 --> 00:02:08.420
zaynen gekumen tsu loyfn mentshn

00:02:08.949 --> 00:02:09.770
fun

00:02:10.046 --> 00:02:11.171
Slabodke.

00:02:12.273 --> 00:02:15.828
Slabodke, dos iz a forshtot fun Kovne

00:02:18.078 --> 00:02:20.531
vu es hobn gelebt a sakh

00:02:20.531 --> 00:02:21.330
yidn.

00:02:22.483 --> 00:02:24.083
ober merstn teyl

00:02:24.083 --> 00:02:25.532
oremere yidn.

00:02:27.258 --> 00:02:29.146
di raykhere hobn gelebt

00:02:29.146 --> 00:02:29.981
merer

00:02:29.981 --> 00:02:30.949
in shtot.

00:02:32.338 --> 00:02:34.222
iz in di Slabodke

00:02:35.038 --> 00:02:36.247
oyf di nakht

00:02:38.177 --> 00:02:41.732
fun finf un tsvantsikstn oyfn zeks un tsvantsikstn

00:02:42.530 --> 00:02:44.803
iz geven der ershter pogrom

00:02:45.939 --> 00:02:48.009
vos hot pasirt in Kovne.

00:02:51.812 --> 00:02:52.940
di mentshn

00:02:52.940 --> 00:02:55.418
vos zaynen antlofn s- fun Slabodke

00:02:56.233 --> 00:02:57.698
tsu undz in shtot

00:02:57.698 --> 00:02:58.758
in tsenter

00:02:59.439 --> 00:03:03.039
hobn gezogt az a gantse nakht hot men oysgeharget

00:03:03.067 --> 00:03:03.905
yidn

00:03:04.282 --> 00:03:05.643
in di shtiber.

00:03:08.552 --> 00:03:11.365
un vi a- mir hobn zikh shpeter dervust

00:03:12.028 --> 00:03:13.912
iz in dem pogrom,

00:03:14.728 --> 00:03:17.102
der ershter vos iz geven in Kovne,

00:03:18.778 --> 00:03:22.232
hot men umgebrakht arum toyznt finf hundert yidn.

00:03:24.465 --> 00:03:26.248
dem Slabodker rov

00:03:29.308 --> 00:03:30.264
hobn

00:03:30.725 --> 00:03:33.302
di banditn

00:03:35.501 --> 00:03:38.229
aruntergezegn mit a zeg di kop

00:03:39.534 --> 00:03:41.520
un avekgeleygt oyfn

00:03:42.032 --> 00:03:43.157
seyfer,

00:03:44.276 --> 00:03:47.544
oyfn khumesh bay vos er iz gezesn un gedavnt.

00:03:50.132 --> 00:03:51.234
un azoy

00:03:51.234 --> 00:03:52.454
fun dem moment

00:03:54.570 --> 00:03:56.370
hot zikh ongehoybn

00:03:57.236 --> 00:03:58.824
undzer umglik,

00:03:58.824 --> 00:04:00.217
undzere tsores.

00:04:04.796 --> 00:04:06.447
s'hobn zikh bavizn

00:04:06.450 --> 00:04:07.575
in shtot

00:04:09.217 --> 00:04:10.426
litviner

00:04:12.542 --> 00:04:15.321
mit vayse bender oyf di hent

00:04:19.460 --> 00:04:20.771
un zey

00:04:21.823 --> 00:04:23.167
mit gever

00:04:24.506 --> 00:04:28.449
hobn zey ongeyner- ongehoybn arumtsugeyn ibern shtot,

00:04:29.298 --> 00:04:30.811
khapn yidn

00:04:33.146 --> 00:04:34.575
un firn

00:04:36.774 --> 00:04:37.713
shisn.

00:04:41.330 --> 00:04:42.846
dem ershte,

00:04:42.883 --> 00:04:44.514
dem ershtn tog

00:04:44.756 --> 00:04:46.809
vos hot pasirt, dos iz geven

00:04:47.760 --> 00:04:49.914
dem zeks un tsvantsikstn,

00:04:51.658 --> 00:04:54.757
hobn zey gekhapt, s'iz do in Kovne iz do

00:04:55.927 --> 00:04:57.322
a garazh

00:04:59.606 --> 00:05:01.423
vu me flegt tsu rekht makhn

00:05:01.867 --> 00:05:02.924
AUTOs.

00:05:04.415 --> 00:05:05.861
in dem garazh

00:05:07.048 --> 00:05:09.658
hobn zey tsuzamengekhapt in shtot

00:05:10.068 --> 00:05:11.868
iber zekhtsik yidn

00:05:13.292 --> 00:05:16.763
un me hot zey dortn in garazh, hot men zey dortn

00:05:16.852 --> 00:05:18.368
tsugeharget

00:05:18.489 --> 00:05:22.685
un tsugeharget oyf a groysn akhzoryesdikn oyfn:

00:05:23.855 --> 00:05:25.604
mit LOPATes,

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:29.318
mit ayzns.

00:05:30.403 --> 00:05:32.338
andere hot men genumen

00:05:32.765 --> 00:05:34.585
un m'hot arayngeshtelt

00:05:34.605 --> 00:05:35.949
a kishke,

00:05:36.410 --> 00:05:38.666
vos me lozt vaser in moyl,

00:05:38.992 --> 00:05:42.007
un gelozn vaser bizkl s'flegt platsn di boykh.

00:05:44.274 --> 00:05:47.576
ot dos hot zikh ongehoybn di shreklekhe teg.

00:05:50.079 --> 00:05:51.575
arum Kovne

00:05:52.357 --> 00:05:54.292
nokh fun tsar's tsaytn

00:05:56.357 --> 00:05:57.819
zaynen geven

00:05:57.977 --> 00:05:59.709
un zaynen nokh itster do

00:06:02.381 --> 00:06:03.220
fortn,

00:06:05.942 --> 00:06:08.468
fun eynem bizn nayntn fort.

00:06:09.772 --> 00:06:11.606
in di ershte teg

00:06:12.759 --> 00:06:15.774
hot men ongehoybn tsuzamenklaybn yidn

00:06:16.235 --> 00:06:19.070
un traybn oyfn zibetn fort.

00:06:22.040 --> 00:06:24.431
men hot dortn far etlekhe teg

00:06:25.584 --> 00:06:27.283
tsuzamengetribn

00:06:28.082 --> 00:06:30.287
arum fir a halb toyznt yidn.

00:06:32.199 --> 00:06:34.826
der fort shteyt in a grobn.

00:06:36.857 --> 00:06:40.074
in dem grobn hot men tsuzamengetribn di yidn.

00:06:40.907 --> 00:06:43.376
di mener hot men gehaltn oyfn gas

00:06:43.376 --> 00:06:44.411
in grobn.

00:06:44.940 --> 00:06:46.557
froyen mit kinder

00:06:46.557 --> 00:06:48.456
arayngetribn in fort.

00:06:49.142 --> 00:06:52.478
der fort, dos iz a oysgegrobener

00:06:53.765 --> 00:06:54.755
roym

00:06:55.807 --> 00:06:59.877
in der erd, bashotn fun oybn mit fil erd.

00:07:00.397 --> 00:07:04.780
un di froyen mit di kinder hot men dortn arayngetribn, zey farmakht,

00:07:05.831 --> 00:07:10.228
nit gegebn esn, nit gegebn trinken, keynem,

00:07:11.906 --> 00:07:12.896
un

00:07:14.015 --> 00:07:15.400
m'hot zey gepaynikt,

00:07:15.400 --> 00:07:16.726
m'hot zey gematert.

00:07:18.285 --> 00:07:19.748
un tsum sof

00:07:21.052 --> 00:07:23.679
hot men alemen oysgeshosn,

00:07:24.731 --> 00:07:27.155
di vos zaynen geven oyfn zibetn fort.

00:07:30.705 --> 00:07:33.748
mir hobn &lt;nokh&gt; dos oykh dervust. es zaynen geven eynike

00:07:33.748 --> 00:07:35.474
vos &lt;s'hot&gt; zikh zey ayngegebn

00:07:35.902 --> 00:07:38.191
tsum antloyfn fun zibetn fort,

00:07:39.395 --> 00:07:41.043
vos zey hobn dertseylt

00:07:42.483 --> 00:07:44.401
dos vos es kumt for.

00:07:45.926 --> 00:07:47.130
un fun zey

00:07:47.130 --> 00:07:48.806
hobn mir farshtanen

00:07:49.031 --> 00:07:51.455
vos es ervart undz oykh.

00:07:54.397 --> 00:07:55.606
nor dos

00:07:56.962 --> 00:07:58.914
alts iz nor geven

00:07:59.713 --> 00:08:01.564
a stikhishe zakh,

00:08:02.531 --> 00:08:04.100
vos zey hobn gemakht

00:08:05.028 --> 00:08:07.132
di litvishe oyfshtendler,

00:08:08.117 --> 00:08:09.360
eyner aleyn.

00:08:11.002 --> 00:08:12.819
az di daytshishe makht

00:08:12.977 --> 00:08:14.102
iz gevorn,

00:08:14.546 --> 00:08:16.127
hot genumen di makht

00:08:16.267 --> 00:08:17.392
in Kovne

00:08:18.191 --> 00:08:19.890
bay ir in di hent,

00:08:21.431 --> 00:08:23.349
hot zikh ongehoybn bavayzn

00:08:23.439 --> 00:08:24.497
bafeln

00:08:25.548 --> 00:08:26.639
vegn yidn:

00:08:27.692 --> 00:08:29.003
vi yidn

00:08:30.088 --> 00:08:31.719
darfn zikh oyffirn,

00:08:33.986 --> 00:08:35.111
vi yidn

00:08:35.858 --> 00:08:37.607
megn geyn in gas,

00:08:39.538 --> 00:08:42.000
vos yidn darfn trogn.

00:08:42.575 --> 00:08:44.054
di ershte zakh

00:08:44.617 --> 00:08:46.215
iz geven a bafel

00:08:46.845 --> 00:08:49.134
az di yidn darfn zikh onton

00:08:49.663 --> 00:08:51.514
gele mogn-dovedn.

00:08:53.240 --> 00:08:55.968
fun fornt eyn mogn-doved oyfn hartsn,

00:08:56.430 --> 00:08:59.006
un oyfn &lt;rugn&gt; a m-, oyfn rukn a mogn-doved,

00:09:00.024 --> 00:09:03.208
vi mir hobn dos ongerufn, di gele lates.

00:09:05.087 --> 00:09:06.769
s'iz aroys a bafel

00:09:07.854 --> 00:09:09.283
az di yidn

00:09:09.812 --> 00:09:11.528
hobn nit keyn rekht

00:09:12.832 --> 00:09:14.649
tsum geyn oyfn lave.

00:09:17.338 --> 00:09:18.913
zey muzn geyn

00:09:18.913 --> 00:09:19.813
nor

00:09:20.848 --> 00:09:23.255
bay breg, baym breg fun gas,

00:09:24.105 --> 00:09:28.301
torn nit geyn eyne lebn di andere, nor darfn geyn nor eyne

00:09:28.458 --> 00:09:30.140
hinter di andern.

00:09:33.487 --> 00:09:35.287
s'iz aroys a bafel

00:09:36.795 --> 00:09:37.549
az

00:09:38.870 --> 00:09:42.071
ver es zol bahaltn yidn fun litviner

00:09:43.325 --> 00:09:44.771
vern oykhet

00:09:44.928 --> 00:09:46.542
bashuldikt in dem

00:09:46.903 --> 00:09:47.825
un

00:09:47.983 --> 00:09:49.901
zey kenen vern ershosn.

00:09:53.501 --> 00:09:54.739
shpeter

00:09:54.750 --> 00:09:56.482
iz aroys a bafel

00:09:57.534 --> 00:09:59.975
az s'vert gegrindet a geto.

00:10:01.905 --> 00:10:05.308
di geto vert gegrindet in di Slabodke,

00:10:05.668 --> 00:10:06.979
in di forshtot

00:10:07.254 --> 00:10:08.362
fun Kovne.

00:10:09.920 --> 00:10:14.167
un s'iz gegebn gevorn a bafel az bizn fuftsetn yuli

00:10:15.050 --> 00:10:17.019
darfn ale yidn

00:10:18.020 --> 00:10:19.364
arayngeyn

00:10:20.349 --> 00:10:21.542
in geto.

00:10:22.104 --> 00:10:26.823
ver es &lt;vet&gt; nit arayngeyn un me vet gefinen, der vert ershosn.

00:10:30.491 --> 00:10:32.612
azoy hot zikh ongehoybn

00:10:33.579 --> 00:10:35.615
der ibervan- -vanderung

00:10:36.785 --> 00:10:37.828
fun

00:10:37.848 --> 00:10:38.956
di yidn

00:10:39.705 --> 00:10:41.370
fun gants Kovne

00:10:41.544 --> 00:10:42.990
in eyn rayon,

00:10:44.750 --> 00:10:46.027
in Slabodke.

00:10:47.754 --> 00:10:52.136
der ort in Slabodke vos m'hot, vos &lt;hot&gt; zikh ongerufn di geto,

00:10:52.850 --> 00:10:54.937
gevorn arumgetsamt

00:10:55.618 --> 00:10:56.945
mit a tsam

00:10:57.086 --> 00:10:58.929
fun shtekhldike drot.

00:11:02.638 --> 00:11:04.894
un beshas m'hot geshtelt di geto

00:11:06.300 --> 00:11:09.804
hot, i- iz gegangen a TSENTRAL'Ne gas

00:11:10.468 --> 00:11:12.774
iz gegangen durkhn geto.

00:11:14.096 --> 00:11:18.667
hobn di daytshn bafoyln tsu makhn i-, fun eyn zayt gas,

00:11:18.667 --> 00:11:20.503
di gas hot geheysn PANERIŲ,

00:11:21.217 --> 00:11:23.054
hobn di daytshn bafoyln

00:11:23.090 --> 00:11:24.699
fun eyn zayt gas

00:11:24.727 --> 00:11:26.409
optsamen di gas

00:11:26.651 --> 00:11:28.755
un fun di ander zayt gas.

00:11:28.980 --> 00:11:30.932
azoy az &lt;s'hot&gt; zikh bakumen

00:11:31.089 --> 00:11:31.778
az

00:11:31.778 --> 00:11:32.669
in

00:11:32.979 --> 00:11:34.745
a teyl fun geto

00:11:34.987 --> 00:11:37.648
iz gevorn opgetsamt fun di gas.

00:11:37.755 --> 00:11:43.014
un &lt;s'hot&gt; zikh bakumen az s'iz gevorn a groyse geto in eyn zayt vu s'iz geven

00:11:43.644 --> 00:11:47.621
merer mentshn, un &lt;s'hot&gt; zikh bakumen de- in der ander zayt fun gas,

00:11:47.930 --> 00:11:49.156
zikh bakumen,

00:11:49.432 --> 00:11:51.502
di azoy gerufene kleyne geto,

00:11:51.963 --> 00:11:53.564
vu s'iz geven a teyl

00:11:53.564 --> 00:11:55.097
vintsiker mentshn

00:11:56.351 --> 00:11:57.273
dortn.

00:11:58.612 --> 00:12:01.323
az mir zaynen aribergeforn, undzer familye,

00:12:02.409 --> 00:12:03.669
in geto

00:12:06.054 --> 00:12:07.955
hot undz tsugenumen

00:12:09.648 --> 00:12:13.051
dem tatn's mit di mame's khaveyrim

00:12:14.947 --> 00:12:16.393
bay zikh in shtub

00:12:18.879 --> 00:12:20.595
in di kleyne geto.

00:12:22.440 --> 00:12:24.881
farshteyt zikh az mentshn hobn zikh gemuzt

00:12:25.612 --> 00:12:28.503
tsuzamenrukn, vayle ort iz geven nit

00:12:28.503 --> 00:12:29.521
keyn sakh.

00:12:29.713 --> 00:12:33.251
un di vos frier hobn gelebt in Slabodke

00:12:33.628 --> 00:12:37.608
hobn gemuzt, oybe zey hobn gehat dray tsimern, tsu fir tsimern,

00:12:37.644 --> 00:12:39.160
hobn zey gemuzt zikh

00:12:39.160 --> 00:12:40.650
arayngeyn in eyn tsimer,

00:12:40.870 --> 00:12:43.420
un dray tsimern ibergebn far di

00:12:43.668 --> 00:12:44.990
vos zaynen arayn

00:12:44.990 --> 00:12:46.464
in geto fun shtot.

00:12:48.933 --> 00:12:53.112
di litviner vos zey hobn gelebt in dem rayon fun di geto

00:12:53.793 --> 00:12:55.829
hobn zikh gebitn

00:12:56.072 --> 00:12:57.335
mit di yidn

00:12:57.371 --> 00:12:58.445
fun shtot.

00:12:58.603 --> 00:13:01.567
zey zaynen avek lebn in di yidishe shtiber,

00:13:02.045 --> 00:13:04.031
un di yidn zaynen avek lebn

00:13:04.290 --> 00:13:05.685
in zeyere shtiber.

00:13:07.344 --> 00:13:08.506
un azoy

00:13:08.506 --> 00:13:10.089
durkh etlekhe vokhn

00:13:10.770 --> 00:13:12.418
zaynen mir ale

00:13:13.065 --> 00:13:14.477
arayn in geto,

00:13:14.769 --> 00:13:15.914
ale yidn

00:13:15.914 --> 00:13:16.788
fun Kovne.

00:13:17.891 --> 00:13:22.864
az arayn in geto umgefer iber draysik toyznt yidn.

00:13:25.738 --> 00:13:28.972
mir hobn zikh nit for- nokh nit forgeshtelt, farshteyt zikh,

00:13:29.231 --> 00:13:30.930
vos es shteyt undz for.

00:13:31.965 --> 00:13:33.934
ober oyf keyn guts

00:13:35.340 --> 00:13:37.105
hobn mir nit ervart.

00:13:39.322 --> 00:13:40.599
fun geto

00:13:40.993 --> 00:13:42.388
hot men ongehoybn

00:13:43.743 --> 00:13:46.117
shafn kolones un traybn

00:13:46.562 --> 00:13:48.193
oyf arbayt.

00:13:51.152 --> 00:13:54.302
iber hoypt hot men getribn arbetn

00:13:55.067 --> 00:13:56.226
oyfn,

00:13:57.007 --> 00:13:59.246
oyf daytsh heyst dos FLUGPLATZ,

00:13:59.808 --> 00:14:01.338
oyfn aerodrom,

00:14:02.458 --> 00:14:06.907
vos di daytshn hobn tsugegreyt dem erodrom far zey, far zeyere

00:14:07.723 --> 00:14:09.067
aeroplanen.

00:14:14.118 --> 00:14:16.866
nor es iz geven, vi me zogt dos,

00:14:16.866 --> 00:14:19.378
azoy bazundere gzeyres.

00:14:20.666 --> 00:14:23.495
azelkhe zakhn. vi s'iz aroys a bafel

00:14:25.121 --> 00:14:28.321
az me darf hobn finf hundert mener

00:14:30.437 --> 00:14:31.849
oyf arbet

00:14:32.833 --> 00:14:35.589
un es darfn zayn inteligentn,

00:14:35.634 --> 00:14:37.096
gelernte,

00:14:39.802 --> 00:14:44.431
vos darfn arbetn bay azelkhe arbet vi in arkhivn,

00:14:44.431 --> 00:14:46.023
in biblyotekn

00:14:46.856 --> 00:14:48.491
un azelkhe zakhn.

00:14:52.644 --> 00:14:54.748
farshteyt zikh az di mentshn

00:14:55.412 --> 00:14:56.503
hobn zikh

00:14:56.846 --> 00:14:58.680
nit gegleybt di daytshn,

00:15:00.137 --> 00:15:00.843
un

00:15:00.843 --> 00:15:04.350
es hobn zikh tsuzamengeklibn nit keyn sakh mentshn.

00:15:05.874 --> 00:15:06.881
dan

00:15:07.950 --> 00:15:09.868
zaynen arayn in geto

00:15:11.139 --> 00:15:12.973
di litvishe politsey,

00:15:15.408 --> 00:15:20.566
un zey zaynen geven ongeton in di forme fun di gevezene litvishe armey.

00:15:23.019 --> 00:15:25.089
un m'hot ongehoybn khapn

00:15:25.297 --> 00:15:26.354
mentshn

00:15:27.592 --> 00:15:29.257
in di finf hundert.

00:15:30.866 --> 00:15:32.261
in dem tog

00:15:34.882 --> 00:15:36.547
bin ikh gegangen,

00:15:37.751 --> 00:15:39.990
ikh hob shoyn gezogt vu mir hobn gelebt

00:15:40.147 --> 00:15:41.677
in di kleyne geto,

00:15:42.037 --> 00:15:44.208
bin ikh gegangen tsu mayn onkl

00:15:44.788 --> 00:15:46.993
vos er hot gelebt in groyse geto.

00:15:49.614 --> 00:15:50.722
tsvishn

00:15:51.318 --> 00:15:55.261
kleyne geto un groyse geto, iber di gas,

00:15:55.588 --> 00:15:57.894
vos di gas hot nit gehert tsu di geto,

00:15:58.085 --> 00:15:59.969
di gas hot gehert tsum shtot,

00:16:00.093 --> 00:16:02.956
un keyn yidn hobn oyf ir nit gehat keyn rekht tsum geyn.

00:16:03.080 --> 00:16:07.209
iz fun kleyne geto in groyse geto iz geven aribergeleygt a brik

00:16:08.261 --> 00:16:14.043
vos mir flegn geyn bri- fun, bay, iber dem brik arayntsugeyn fun kleyne geto glaykh in groyse geto.

00:16:16.226 --> 00:16:17.419
az ikh bin

00:16:18.015 --> 00:16:19.191
gegangen,

00:16:19.297 --> 00:16:21.856
bin ariber dem brik fun di kleyne geto,

00:16:23.583 --> 00:16:24.703
un ikh gey

00:16:24.703 --> 00:16:26.312
in di groyse geto.

00:16:27.077 --> 00:16:29.704
ikh gib a kuk, es geyen tsu tsu mir

00:16:31.380 --> 00:16:33.281
a litvisher soldat

00:16:34.164 --> 00:16:36.217
un a yidisher politsist,

00:16:38.872 --> 00:16:43.630
vos zey zaynen gegangen tsuzamenklaybn in di kolone di finf hundert mentshn.

00:16:46.280 --> 00:16:47.540
der litvisher

00:16:47.934 --> 00:16:49.042
soldat

00:16:49.740 --> 00:16:51.287
hot mir opgeshtelt

00:16:53.030 --> 00:16:55.691
un er fregt bayn yidishn politsyant:

00:16:57.553 --> 00:16:59.049
"dem veln mir nemen?"

00:17:01.603 --> 00:17:03.504
ikh bin damolst geven

00:17:04.774 --> 00:17:06.034
fuftsn yor.

00:17:08.724 --> 00:17:10.862
ikh bin geven in kleyner vuks.

00:17:12.470 --> 00:17:14.298
kh'hob oysgezen nokh vi a,

00:17:14.298 --> 00:17:16.109
me zogt dos, vi a kind.

00:17:18.072 --> 00:17:23.011
zogt der litvisher politsyant, "nu," zogt er, "vos zoln mir nemen?" zogt er. "er iz dokh nokh a kind.

00:17:23.895 --> 00:17:25.391
vos vet er ton vos?

00:17:28.062 --> 00:17:29.880
er iz dokh &lt;nu,&gt; nit keyn arbeter

00:17:30.054 --> 00:17:31.030
un nit keyn

00:17:31.050 --> 00:17:32.310
inteligent."

00:17:33.851 --> 00:17:36.140
hot er &lt;zikh&gt; ayngekukt oyf mir, der soldat.

00:17:36.804 --> 00:17:38.081
"nu," zogt er, "gey."

00:17:40.989 --> 00:17:42.890
dos iz geven dem ershtn mol

00:17:44.347 --> 00:17:46.619
vos mayn mazl

00:17:47.064 --> 00:17:49.185
hot mir geratevet fun toyt.

00:17:50.810 --> 00:17:54.365
vayle az m'hot tsuzamengeklibn iber finf hundert mener

00:17:56.379 --> 00:17:57.892
hot men di mener

00:17:58.134 --> 00:17:59.529
avekgetribn

00:18:00.092 --> 00:18:01.892
oyfn firtn fort

00:18:02.994 --> 00:18:04.996
in a forshtot oykh fun

00:18:05.475 --> 00:18:07.393
Kovne, in PANEMUNĖ,

00:18:08.394 --> 00:18:11.223
un men hot zey dortn alemen oysgeshosn.

00:18:21.033 --> 00:18:22.617
der tsveyter fal

00:18:22.620 --> 00:18:23.846
fun a masn,

00:18:24.678 --> 00:18:26.124
a masn-shisn.

00:18:27.834 --> 00:18:29.178
dos iz geven

00:18:32.812 --> 00:18:34.865
az der komendant

00:18:35.377 --> 00:18:36.485
fun geto

00:18:37.082 --> 00:18:38.511
hot gezogt

00:18:39.174 --> 00:18:41.420
az in a rayon fun geto hot men

00:18:41.420 --> 00:18:42.729
oyf im geshosn.

00:18:44.895 --> 00:18:46.712
yidn hobn geshosn oyf im.

00:18:48.000 --> 00:18:50.357
hot men arumgeringlt dem rayon,

00:18:51.678 --> 00:18:54.441
di litvishe soldatn mit daytshn,

00:18:56.673 --> 00:18:59.199
un m'hot aroysgetribn fun di shtiber

00:19:02.040 --> 00:19:03.216
froyen,

00:19:03.356 --> 00:19:04.414
kinder,

00:19:04.942 --> 00:19:06.523
eltere mentshn.

00:19:08.013 --> 00:19:12.311
mener merstn teyl zaynen geven oyf der arbet; dos iz geven in mitn tog.

00:19:14.274 --> 00:19:16.440
un m'hot tsuzamengeklibn oykh

00:19:16.440 --> 00:19:19.196
iber onderhalbn toyznt azelkhe,

00:19:20.231 --> 00:19:21.677
aza grupe,

00:19:23.336 --> 00:19:27.633
un men hot zey aroysgefirt un avekgefirt oyfn nayntn fort

00:19:30.575 --> 00:19:32.780
vu me hot zey alemen oysgeshosn.

00:19:33.410 --> 00:19:36.877
farshteyt zikh, di daytshn hobn nit gezogt az m'hot geshosn.

00:19:37.258 --> 00:19:40.627
daytshn hobn gezogt az m'hot zey aribergefirt

00:19:41.662 --> 00:19:44.736
in an ander ort oyf arbayt.

00:19:46.708 --> 00:19:50.331
nor in geto hot men zikh dervust, m'hot farshtanen,

00:19:52.040 --> 00:19:53.387
az dos

00:19:53.387 --> 00:19:54.273
fun zey

00:19:54.318 --> 00:19:55.983
zaynen shoyn keyner nishto.

00:19:58.098 --> 00:20:00.894
ven dos iz gevezn di

00:20:02.081 --> 00:20:03.206
di aktsye?

00:20:03.245 --> 00:20:04.421
dos iz geven

00:20:04.715 --> 00:20:06.767
in umgefer

00:20:06.767 --> 00:20:08.715
in

00:20:08.715 --> 00:20:12.224
in yor eyn un fer- toyznt nayn hundert eyn un fertsik,

00:20:14.750 --> 00:20:17.767
in yuli monat.

00:20:17.767 --> 00:20:19.206
yuli monat

00:20:19.206 --> 00:20:21.662
tsu onheyb AVGUST. ikh gedenk shoyn nit.

00:20:28.912 --> 00:20:31.370
un faktish iz dos geven

00:20:33.418 --> 00:20:35.136
di ershte gresere g-

00:20:35.136 --> 00:20:36.517
aktsye in geto.

00:20:36.928 --> 00:20:39.757
oybe nit rekhenen di finf hundert mentshn,

00:20:39.915 --> 00:20:41.960
mener vos m'hot aroysgefirt

00:20:41.960 --> 00:20:43.105
un geshosn,

00:20:43.105 --> 00:20:45.934
vos dos iz geven oykh an aktsye, di finf hundert mener.

00:20:46.277 --> 00:20:48.971
ober dos iz nokh nit geven azoy

00:20:49.652 --> 00:20:51.333
a masn-zakh.

00:20:56.047 --> 00:20:57.459
dem firtn

00:20:57.988 --> 00:20:59.197
oktober

00:21:00.873 --> 00:21:02.099
in der fri

00:21:03.641 --> 00:21:05.104
vi ikh hob shoyn gezogt

00:21:05.868 --> 00:21:09.069
az undzer familye iz geven in di kleyne geto,

00:21:12.888 --> 00:21:15.633
zaynen mir oyfgeshtanen in der fri

00:21:18.828 --> 00:21:20.763
un mir hobn gezen shoyn

00:21:20.921 --> 00:21:22.350
durkh di fentster

00:21:23.942 --> 00:21:26.484
az in kleyne geto marshirn arayn

00:21:26.760 --> 00:21:28.628
groyse opteylungen

00:21:29.375 --> 00:21:32.424
fun daytshishe un litvishe mini- militer.

00:21:34.286 --> 00:21:36.238
mir hobn nokh nit farshtanen

00:21:36.868 --> 00:21:38.263
far vos dos iz.

00:21:41.154 --> 00:21:43.190
nor zey, mir hobn gezen

00:21:44.512 --> 00:21:45.553
az zey

00:21:46.942 --> 00:21:50.413
hobn zikh fanandergeteylt in di kleyne geto

00:21:50.857 --> 00:21:52.348
un ongehoybn

00:21:52.359 --> 00:21:54.193
geyn iber ale shtiber.

00:21:56.983 --> 00:21:58.834
un m'iz arayn in di shtub

00:21:59.058 --> 00:22:00.824
vu mir hobn gelebt oykh.

00:22:01.067 --> 00:22:02.853
m'hot ongehoybn alemen

00:22:02.853 --> 00:22:04.149
aroystraybn

00:22:05.150 --> 00:22:07.169
fun di shtiber, ale yidn,

00:22:11.040 --> 00:22:12.097
un

00:22:14.432 --> 00:22:15.473
traybn

00:22:17.216 --> 00:22:20.552
i- oyf, in, ah, tsuzamen in kolones.

00:22:20.979 --> 00:22:23.707
yo, ikh darf nokh dermonen eyn zakh.

00:22:24.540 --> 00:22:26.250
azoy vi mayn tate

00:22:26.278 --> 00:22:28.179
iz geven a shnayder

00:22:29.703 --> 00:22:31.115
un in

00:22:31.458 --> 00:22:33.152
geto iz geven

00:22:33.197 --> 00:22:34.423
geshafn

00:22:35.762 --> 00:22:36.651
an

00:22:36.842 --> 00:22:38.358
ÄLTESTENRAT

00:22:38.358 --> 00:22:40.093
un an ARBEITSAMT,

00:22:41.111 --> 00:22:43.890
hot men im mayn tatn in ARBEITSAMT

00:22:44.148 --> 00:22:45.357
gegebn

00:22:46.359 --> 00:22:48.877
a shayn, vi me ruft dos onet.

00:22:48.941 --> 00:22:50.201
a dokument.

00:22:51.658 --> 00:22:53.120
s'iz geven der

00:22:54.189 --> 00:22:56.850
daytsh vos hot ongefirt mit di geto,

00:22:57.159 --> 00:22:59.313
geven zayn familye JORDAN.

00:23:00.618 --> 00:23:02.857
hot men ongerufn di shaynen

00:23:03.065 --> 00:23:04.345
vos m'hot gegebn

00:23:04.348 --> 00:23:05.557
di fakh-layt

00:23:06.423 --> 00:23:08.763
hot men ongerufn JORDAN-shaynen.

00:23:11.351 --> 00:23:12.999
iz mayn tate

00:23:13.207 --> 00:23:15.159
hot gehat aza shayn.

00:23:16.683 --> 00:23:18.351
az me hot undz getribn

00:23:18.351 --> 00:23:20.998
in kleyn-geto fun di shtiber

00:23:23.265 --> 00:23:25.571
un m'hot undz getribn

00:23:26.270 --> 00:23:29.790
tsuzamengeshtelt in kolones, hot mayn tate

00:23:29.897 --> 00:23:30.921
un nokh

00:23:31.550 --> 00:23:32.332
yidn

00:23:32.332 --> 00:23:34.464
vos hobn gehat azelkhe shaynen

00:23:34.858 --> 00:23:36.320
hobn zey gevizn

00:23:36.900 --> 00:23:39.291
zeyer shayn az zey hobn JORDAN-shaynen.

00:23:40.123 --> 00:23:41.518
hot men zey

00:23:41.591 --> 00:23:43.577
opgeteylt fun di,

00:23:44.780 --> 00:23:46.361
fun di kolones

00:23:46.755 --> 00:23:48.026
un m'hot zey

00:23:48.026 --> 00:23:50.512
avekgeshtelt in an ander grupe.

00:23:51.868 --> 00:23:54.073
dortn iz geven a mark, hot men

00:23:54.416 --> 00:23:55.423
undz

00:23:56.272 --> 00:23:59.068
alemen, di vos hobn gehat di JORDAN-shaynen,

00:23:59.175 --> 00:24:02.781
heyst dos di, der fakh-layt mit di familye,

00:24:02.837 --> 00:24:04.721
hot men opgeshtelt bazunder.

00:24:05.992 --> 00:24:08.703
un di, ale vos zey hobn nit gehat keyn shaynen

00:24:08.895 --> 00:24:11.060
hot men getribn in kolones,

00:24:11.105 --> 00:24:13.394
un m'hot aroysgetribn fun geto,

00:24:15.543 --> 00:24:18.035
un m'hot zey aropgeshtelt oyf a plats

00:24:18.868 --> 00:24:20.600
nit vayt fun geto,

00:24:20.893 --> 00:24:22.457
zey tsuzamengeklibn.

00:24:22.985 --> 00:24:25.775
dort-, azoy hot men tsuzamengeklibn zey

00:24:25.787 --> 00:24:27.891
arum fir a halb toyznt

00:24:28.706 --> 00:24:30.354
fun di kleyne geto.

00:24:33.380 --> 00:24:34.404
undz

00:24:34.697 --> 00:24:36.261
mit di JORDAN-shaynen

00:24:37.650 --> 00:24:41.104
hot men alemen genumen, un m'hot fun di kleyne geto

00:24:41.835 --> 00:24:44.715
aribergetribn in di groyse geto

00:24:45.193 --> 00:24:46.571
ibern brik

00:24:47.201 --> 00:24:50.070
vos iz geven tsvishn kleyne geto un groyse geto,

00:24:50.430 --> 00:24:54.401
hot men undz alemen aribergetribn in kleyn- in di groyse geto,

00:24:54.626 --> 00:24:57.641
un m'hot zikh undz geheysn zukhn erter vu tsum

00:24:58.389 --> 00:24:59.295
voynen.

00:25:01.562 --> 00:25:02.687
un di

00:25:02.912 --> 00:25:05.573
vos m'hot opgeteylt fun di kleyne geto

00:25:06.708 --> 00:25:08.913
hot men zey alemen, di daytshn

00:25:09.797 --> 00:25:12.525
hobn dos alts filmirt, fotografirt.

00:25:15.213 --> 00:25:19.916
ober zey hobn gefilmirt azoy, az s'iz oysgekumen az nor litviner

00:25:20.040 --> 00:25:21.311
traybn di yidn.

00:25:21.311 --> 00:25:23.527
nit di daytshn, nor di litviner.

00:25:25.878 --> 00:25:31.390
un nakher hot men zey shpeter di ale araynge- -lozn tsurik in kleyne geto.

00:25:33.320 --> 00:25:34.833
ober in

00:25:35.058 --> 00:25:36.656
fir teg arum

00:25:37.910 --> 00:25:39.637
hot men vayter alemen

00:25:39.637 --> 00:25:41.094
tsuzamengeklibn,

00:25:41.876 --> 00:25:43.727
di vos zaynen geven in kleyne geto,

00:25:44.762 --> 00:25:47.051
un m'hot zey aroysgefirt oyfn fort

00:25:47.681 --> 00:25:49.346
un alemen geshosn.

00:25:51.849 --> 00:25:55.033
azoy az dos iz di, geven di kleyne aktsye,

00:25:57.992 --> 00:26:00.197
un dan zaynen umgekumen

00:26:01.417 --> 00:26:02.660
fir a halb

00:26:03.054 --> 00:26:05.508
toyznt yidn.

00:26:06.362 --> 00:26:08.415
vu ir

00:26:06.683 --> 00:26:10.050
mener, froyen, kinder, alemen.

00:26:08.775 --> 00:26:12.179
vu ir gelebt in, in kleynem geto ven iz gevezn?

00:26:13.162 --> 00:26:14.760
in kleynem geto

00:26:16.436 --> 00:26:18.472
az m'hot undz aribergesh- -tribn

00:26:20.688 --> 00:26:23.365
iz vayter hot undz tsugenumen

00:26:23.473 --> 00:26:25.256
mayn mame's a khaverte,

00:26:29.109 --> 00:26:30.010
vos zey

00:26:30.010 --> 00:26:33.120
zeyer familye hot gelebt oyf tsvey tsimern.

00:26:35.117 --> 00:26:37.845
hot zi undz opgegebn eyn tsimer.

00:26:41.259 --> 00:26:43.580
un mir hobn zikh dortn bazetst.

00:26:46.912 --> 00:26:48.712
nu, in di tsayt

00:26:49.629 --> 00:26:50.360
hot men,

00:26:50.360 --> 00:26:52.830
farshteyt zikh, m'iz in shtub nit gezesn.

00:26:55.248 --> 00:26:57.886
men hot getribn oyf arbet

00:26:57.886 --> 00:27:01.520
in kolones, &lt;m'hot zikh&gt; geshafn kolones, di daytshn hobn gemakht

00:27:03.129 --> 00:27:05.520
vu me hot zey gedarft.

00:27:07.652 --> 00:27:09.047
mayn tate

00:27:09.187 --> 00:27:11.510
als fakh-man, als shnayder,

00:27:12.900 --> 00:27:15.510
iz gegangen in di kolone

00:27:16.072 --> 00:27:17.416
fun fakh-mener

00:27:17.743 --> 00:27:19.948
bay di daytshishe politsey.

00:27:21.236 --> 00:27:23.812
zey hobn zikh ongerufn N.S.K.K.

00:27:25.472 --> 00:27:27.036
dortn iz geven

00:27:30.045 --> 00:27:31.018
a

00:27:31.800 --> 00:27:33.240
maysterskaye,

00:27:33.240 --> 00:27:34.461
&lt;vi&gt; mir zogn dos,

00:27:35.580 --> 00:27:39.607
vos m'hot geneyt far di daytshn, men hot tsu rekht gemakht

00:27:41.418 --> 00:27:42.678
zeyere

00:27:44.625 --> 00:27:45.767
zakhn.

00:27:46.683 --> 00:27:49.226
nu, zey hobn ge- alts geneyt dos vos di daytshn

00:27:49.856 --> 00:27:50.998
flegn zogn.

00:27:54.362 --> 00:27:55.234
ikh

00:27:56.589 --> 00:27:58.220
bin nor damolst geven

00:27:58.985 --> 00:28:02.557
vi me ru- vi m'hot dos ongerufn, nit keyn arbets-feiker.

00:28:03.778 --> 00:28:07.620
un ikh hob &lt;dokh&gt; nit gerekhnt az ikh darf shoyn geyn arbetn far zikh

00:28:08.756 --> 00:28:10.084
als a yingl.

00:28:12.401 --> 00:28:15.146
farshteyt zikh, es iz geven a problem

00:28:15.742 --> 00:28:16.681
in

00:28:16.755 --> 00:28:17.711
geto

00:28:18.476 --> 00:28:19.601
mitn esn.

00:28:20.703 --> 00:28:23.954
vayle mm esn hot men gegebn zeyer vintsik,

00:28:24.585 --> 00:28:26.976
un mentshn hobn zeyer gehungert.

00:28:29.175 --> 00:28:31.214
hot zikh geshafn aza

00:28:31.217 --> 00:28:32.156
zakh

00:28:33.107 --> 00:28:34.468
vi es zaynen geven

00:28:34.592 --> 00:28:38.046
mentshn vos zey hobn ye gehat vos tsum esn.

00:28:38.709 --> 00:28:41.319
ober zey hobn nit geda- gevelt geyn

00:28:42.675 --> 00:28:45.943
arbetn oyfn erodrom, vayle oyfn erodrom

00:28:47.180 --> 00:28:48.291
iz geven

00:28:48.291 --> 00:28:50.982
a shlekhter ort tsum arbetn.
